import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import Coin from "./routes/Coin"
import Coins from "./routes/Coins"

const Router = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/*" element={<Coins />} />
        <Route path="/:coinId" element={<Coin />} />
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default Router
